Code preview of the table TB_REVIEW

drop table if exists TB_REVIEW;

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: TB_REVIEW */
/*==============================================================*/
create table TB_REVIEW
(
ORG_ID int(8) not null comment '组织id',
REVIEW_ID int(8) not null comment '审核流水id',
NEWS_ID INT(10) not null comment '审核id',
ORG_OPER INT(8) comment '机构审核用户',
ORG_RESULT NVARCHAR(200) comment '机构审核结果',
ORG_CREATE_TIME DATETIME comment '机构审核时间',
ORG_REVIEW INT(2) comment '机构审核状态',
BRANCH_OPER_ID INT(8) comment '支部审核人',
BRANCH_CREATE_TIME DATETIME comment '支部审核时间',
BRANCH_REVIEW_RESULT INT(2) comment '支部审核状态',
BRANCH_RESULT NVARCHAR(200) comment '支部审核结果',
primary key (ORG_ID, REVIEW_ID)
);

alter table TB_REVIEW comment '审核表';
